Packages
Database Provides all the necessary logic to read, write, and update information in the sql database used to store user information.
GameObject Provides all the objects required during the GamePlay state of the game.
GameObject.ArtificialIntelligence Provides the logic for the movement and AI requirements of the 8 different enemies present in the game.
GamePlay Provides the structures used to manage the GamePlay state of the game.
Menu Provides the views and models used during the Menu state of the game.
SystemController Provides the high level structures that initialize the game and switch between the Menu state and the GamePlay state of the game.
